我無肌肉痛 做個陣痛 但做完翌日唔會有感覺。。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T12:42:59.000Z","msg":"做嗰陣痛通常係乳酸痛<br />\n做完翌日痛嗰啲叫遲發性酸痛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T13:03:56.000Z","msg":"咁即係做個陣有痛 都有肌肉增長？"},{"pid":"d1612c6277ace5dbaf7bfe6ba0c3391a5a16facb","tid":1084292,"uid":46323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T13:06:37.000Z","msg":"斷食5個月減18kg 減7％體脂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef8c7a41111fb2666626486ba8215d187898fbe6","tid":1084292,"uid":110135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1612c6277ace5dbaf7bfe6ba0c3391a5a16facb","tid":1084292,"uid":46323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T13:06:37.000Z","msg":"斷食5個月減18kg 減7％體脂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T13:09:34.000Z","msg":"點樣斷食法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ae40424fd3fec2f36790b2dcc9ea800a27b38c3","tid":1084292,"uid":186071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T13:14:12.000Z","msg":"正正經經操肌<br />\n唔飲甜野<br />\n一星期 兩三 次有氧已經夠<br />\n<br />\n最會d你講我係減脂 唔想練大隻<br />\n講到操幾下 就會大咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"947d5d2a42479f4656b7e588351af1b3a92029b3","tid":1084292,"uid":110135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ae40424fd3fec2f36790b2dcc9ea800a27b38c3","tid":1084292,"uid":186071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T13:14:12.000Z","msg":"正正經經操肌<br />\n唔飲甜野<br />\n一星期 兩三 次有氧已經夠<br />\n<br />\n最會d你講我係減脂 唔想練大隻<br />\n講到操幾下 就會大咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T13:29:48.000Z","msg":"戒左甜野，同埋我無講我唔係唔想練肌肉<br />\n我上面我講我係有做workout 練腹肌同butt<br />\n同埋有舉啞鈴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2e6ed3f38e9f0dee316854b9ad456510008d9c4","tid":1084292,"uid":46323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef8c7a41111fb2666626486ba8215d187898fbe6","tid":1084292,"uid":110135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1612c6277ace5dbaf7bfe6ba0c3391a5a16facb","tid":1084292,"uid":46323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T13:06:37.000Z","msg":"斷食5個月減18kg 減7％體脂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T13:09:34.000Z","msg":"點樣斷食法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T13:35:01.000Z","msg":"我set所有野係10至4點內食哂，其他時間1卡都唔食<br />\n多數一餐食哂一日要既營養就完全唔食<br />\n<br />\n開頭個三個月冇限卡路里，都冇做運動<br />\n<br />\n去到TDEE已經接近我吸收量就平台期左一個月<br />\n<br />\n之後開始限卡路里同做運動<br />\n主食係魚，海鮮，豆腐，菇，麵豉湯之類<br />\n壓到1400卡一日咁<br />\n<br />\n每日做消300到400卡既Cardio<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n覺得食野入手係重要過work out好多<br />\n<br />\n以前遊過水，做過weight training<br />\n都冇我依家if咁快同有效<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K0wwOzC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK0wwOzC.jpg&h=76a36a88&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1dacf23959586ec687f2bbeed317d3aac25219af","tid":1084292,"uid":158977,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9aa87248ad830e96ad45bc36af4281ba083da838","tid":1084292,"uid":227262,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T10:12:14.000Z","msg":"之前讀U係hall有gym房，然後見得閒又想減肥，每日跑10k加1個半鐘器械，無特登計劃飲食（餐餐食雞胸飲豆漿唔食飯嗰D癡線野），想食咩就食咩，但係食完要減翻卡路里，兩個月重左7kg，唔係代表肥左，其實係因為肌肉比脂肪重<br />\n<br />\n節食係唔得，反而會傷身，你可以試下計卡路里，計下你每日消耗幾多，然後低過消耗量都可以減肥<br />\n<br />\n仲有千祈唔好食宵夜同熬夜，仲有如果食嘅卡路里凸左就一定要做gym減翻佢，同埋一定要穩定，舉例，你每日要消耗係3000卡路里，然後你吸收2500，啫係每日減500，如果你有日吸收多左減唔到500，就最少運動到翻依個數<br />\n<br />\n如果你忍唔到口嘅話，你記住一個乾炒牛河嘅卡路里係慢跑20k左右，你一直咁諗就唔會想食3高嘅野<br />\n<br />\n其實我講嘅都係阿媽係女人嘅道理，就睇你有無耐力持之以恆做<br />\n<br />\n利申：有健身牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T13:36:20.000Z","msg":"10k cls 乜柒都俾你燒晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"114ea376e8a8a5a6ef5dc7227b9ba842806d8b0a","tid":1084292,"uid":107881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5300dbac1423dd7a3c17ecbc5367c38ee001ba0","tid":1084292,"uid":110135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c693696179472a9aee32ac69378bf99e3bc89846","tid":1084292,"uid":107881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a01f988735ec11bb2b4f65ef99e50886546d34f","tid":1084292,"uid":110135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T12:07:33.000Z","msg":"但我無肌肉痛 做個陣痛 但做完翌日唔會有感覺。。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T12:42:59.000Z","msg":"做嗰陣痛通常係乳酸痛<br />\n做完翌日痛嗰啲叫遲發性酸痛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T13:03:56.000Z","msg":"咁即係做個陣有痛 都有肌肉增長？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T13:43:05.000Z","msg":"no 只係你做嗰段時間乳酸積累係肌肉入面<br />\n<br />\n痛唔痛唔係一個肌肉增長嘅指標，個個人嘅反應都唔同"},{"pid":"327d4b3ece95356ff79d985710cdd5e4d3ee7d5e","tid":1084292,"uid":186071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"947d5d2a42479f4656b7e588351af1b3a92029b3","tid":1084292,"uid":110135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ae40424fd3fec2f36790b2dcc9ea800a27b38c3","tid":1084292,"uid":186071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T13:14:12.000Z","msg":"正正經經操肌<br />\n唔飲甜野<br />\n一星期 兩三 次有氧已經夠<br />\n<br />\n最會d你講我係減脂 唔想練大隻<br />\n講到操幾下 就會大咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T13:29:48.000Z","msg":"戒左甜野，同埋我無講我唔係唔想練肌肉<br />\n我上面我講我係有做workout 練腹肌同butt<br />\n同埋有舉啞鈴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T13:46:15.000Z","msg":"不如講下 你平時點做<br />\n<br />\n係咪十下內 做到最大重量？<br />\n即係最後個下 係已經冇曬力<br />\n<br />\n定鳩舉 十幾下 就算？"},{"pid":"44ff795174082607a09024be228ec87748e77907","tid":1084292,"uid":186071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime"